citeinfo.title: TownofWhitby_Wards

descript.abstract: Town of Whitby ward locations with councillor name and contact phone number.
descript.purpose: The Whitby wards shapefile allows Town of Whitby staff and the public to determine which ward a property is in. This allows staff and residents to contact the appropriate councillor for their property.

place.placekey: Corporation of the Town of Whitby

idinfo.accconst: Internal Staff of the Town of Whitby. Not to be used by external agencies unless outlined in a data sharing agreement.
idinfo.useconst: Internal Staff at the Town of Whitby and the general public may view the Whitby Wards Shapefile but editing of this shapefile is to be done by the GIS Coordinator.
